Hahaha, well, I wanted to know why I had to pick 21 to show 18 results <img src="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/images/smilies/icon_e_wink.gif" alt=";-)" title="Wink" /> Indeed, icon size changes things, but then Minimum Menu Height is not the minimum number of search results, because otherwise the icon size would just make the menu bigger for the same minimum. Oh well, we shall never know what that setting really is; perhaps just a base number of pixels multiplied by the value we give...<br /><br />Best Regards,<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=22972">Sylvain</a> — Tue Aug 22, 2017 8:31 pm</p><hr />
